{"type":"message","id":"22183861","parentId":"a2f17bd5","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:18:12.830Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uNQwmbhzYPlXmFw5WcpOs0D1|fc_043231cc2d932b930169d0ad23687c819ba63f55c3d45e381e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 2026-04-03: Verified memory-lancedb-pro plugin by successful store+recall roundtrip after slight indexing delay.\n- 2026-04-03: Skills audit found core/Feishu/web_fetch largely available; web_search blocked by missing Brave API key; browser subsystem enabled but not ready.\n- 2026-04-03: CTF skill files are installed, but practical toolchain is largely missing (gdb/pwntools/z3/sqlmap/ffuf and others absent).\n- 2026-04-03: Initialized self-improving system under ~/self-improving and added workspace operating guides: WORKSTATE, DIAGNOSTICS, RISK_TIERS, CHECKPOINTS, PLAN_MODE, APPROVAL_PATTERNS, RESUME_FLOW, EVIDENCE_RULES, OUTPUT_SHAPES, QUESTION_STRATEGY, FAILURE_HANDLING, STYLE_PREFERENCES, TASK_SELECTION, MEMORY_HYGIENE, ESCALATION_RULES, COMPOUNDING_LOOP.\n- 2026-04-03: Learned from uploaded Claude Code source mainly at workflow/design level: layered diagnostics, explicit plan mode, resumable work-state, risk-aware approvals, evidence-based confidence, and memory layering.\n- 2026-04-03: Browser/gateway investigation: loopback bind is correct for local-only use, but gateway/browser chain remained unhealthy; pending pairing request was approved successfully, RPC probe recovered to ok, yet browser still not ready and gateway sessions still closed/handshake timed out.\n- 2026-04-03: web_search issue was conclusively external: missing BRAVE_API_KEY; user could not obtain key due to network restrictions, so that repair path was intentionally abandoned.\n- 2026-04-03: Successfully fetched Yaohuo tea-house latest posts over HTTP by directly reading board page /bbs/book_list.aspx?siteid=1000&classid=177 using existing local cookies; skill helper script could not run because Python dependency curl_